articles.description: American singer and actor Meat Loaf has died at the age of 74.
articles.content:
American singer and actor Meat Loaf, real name Michael Lee Aday, has died at the age of 74. The Grammy winner died Thursday night with his wife, Deborah, by his side, reports Deadline.
